{"id":677670,"date":[{"year":1984,"month":7,"day":3}],"page":"3","source":"《知识窗》","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"社会大学","column":"","genre":"","count":"99","ytitle":"","mtitle":"自学十忌","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一忌选择学科不当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二忌好高骛远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三忌“常立志”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四忌“本本主义”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五忌“单打一”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六忌固执己见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七忌自暴自弃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八忌漫无目的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九忌浅尝辄止。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十忌骄傲自满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(肖应摘自《知识窗》1984年第2期)"}]}